And the idea here is
that will stay up.

00:22:02.330 --> 00:22:05.615
So as you keep on horizontally
swiping to the next photos in

00:22:05.615 --> 00:22:09.090
the set, that'll stay up, and
it'll just switch over.

00:22:09.090 --> 00:22:11.560
Similarly, if you hit the Info
icon next to it, the idea is

00:22:11.560 --> 00:22:12.770
it'll occupy the same space.

00:22:12.770 --> 00:22:15.000
You could have the fun animation
of it, perhaps

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:16.330
rotating around, showing
you some

00:22:16.330 --> 00:22:18.520
information about the photo.

00:22:18.520 --> 00:22:21.800
And what we've done here is I
feel like having this overlay

00:22:21.800 --> 00:22:25.510
information rather than that
obscuring pop-up, it really

00:22:25.510 --> 00:22:28.310
takes better advantage of the
screen real estate available

00:22:28.310 --> 00:22:30.280
on the tablet because you can
still see a large amount of

00:22:30.280 --> 00:22:33.500
the image, which is what this
is all about, and then get

00:22:33.500 --> 00:22:35.672
your comments experience
as well.

00:22:35.672 --> 00:22:36.890
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah, awesome.

