the quick contacts, you can have
the profile icon actually

00:23:10.890 --> 00:23:13.170
jump you there as well if you
decide that quick contacts

00:23:13.170 --> 00:23:15.550
isn't for you.

00:23:15.550 --> 00:23:17.445
NICK BUTCHER: If the author's
watching, this is also a

